Porro Corp talk sey e go buy back as many as one million common share.

Di manufacturer of chemical, and industrial materials, e no talk how much e go pay, and when e go do di transaction.

Erro also yarn sey e go cancel di unused portion of a 1987 buy back plan for admin.

Di plan dey call for di company to buy back 2,250,000 share wey reflect three four million stock loss last year.

So far di company don buy back 1.6 million share.

For New York Stock Exchange, Ferro close at $25.25, down 50 cents.

